# Research Log

Track every research project for compound knowledge building. Each entry links back to the project folder and forward to questions it generated.

---

## Log Format

### [Date] — [Research Question]
- **Framework used:** [from [[research-frameworks]]]
- **Depth level:** [Quick Scan / Standard / Deep Dive]
- **Key findings:** [2-3 bullet points]
- **Surprises:** [what did you NOT expect to find?]
- **Open questions generated:** [links to [[open-questions]] that could become future projects]
- **Project folder:** [[projects/project-name]]
- **Concepts added:** [new entries in [[concepts]]]
- **Data points added:** [count of new entries in [[data-points]]]

---

## Projects

(entries accumulate here as you complete research projects)
